The Java implementation of CVSS v4.0 in this project (CvssV4.java, 
CvssV4Lookup.java, CvssV4MaxSeverity.java, CvssV4MaxComposed.java) is an 
independent implementation written in Java, based on the specification and 
reference implementation above. This Java code is licensed under the Apache 
License 2.0, consistent with the rest of this project.
